Description: Transform your Hyprland desktop into Windows 11
 Hyprland Undercover transforms your Hyprland desktop into a convincing
 Windows 11 environment with a single command. It includes a Windows 11-style
 taskbar (Waybar), start menu (Rofi/Wofi), and matching themes.
 .
 Features:
  - One-click transformation between native Hyprland and Windows 11 look
  - Automatic backup and restore of original configurations
  - Windows 11-style taskbar via Waybar
  - Windows 11-style start menu via Rofi/Wofi
  - GTK4/Libadwaita settings application
